        "zh": "1.IT零售現代化資料平台<br>2.雲端技術與零售流程<br>3.零售數位化工作區<br>4.消費資訊安全平台<br>5.物聯網與智慧零售<br>6.數位看板與智慧零售<br>7.影像分析與智慧零售<br>8.消費者行為與AI決策<br>9.智慧型自動販賣機<br>10 無人化商店",
        "en": "1.Retail Modernization &amp; IT Technology<br>2.Cloud technology &amp; retail processes<br>3.Retail digitalization workspace<br>4.Consumer information security<br>5.Internet of Things &amp; Smart Retail<br>6.Digital signage &amp; Smart Retail<br>7.Image analysis &amp; Smart Retail<br>8.Consumer behavior &amp; AI technology<br>9.Smart vending machine<br>10.Unmanned store"
